Class InfluenceLayerTemplates

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.cuni.mff.kocur.influence.InfluenceLayerTemplates

    public class InfluenceLayerTemplates
extends java.lang.Object
implements cz.cuni.mff.kocur.events.FrameworkEventListener
    Class that stores influence layers, that do not change during the application. For example radiant towers and base generate a field, that can help ais to navigate to safer zone.
    Author:
    kocur
